Exemplo 1 | ci-sum-2025Exemplo 2 | postgresExemplo 3 | nginx <p>Clone o repositório: <pre><code>git clone https://github.com/gustavokubiack/ci-sum-2025.git
cd ci-sum-2025/
</code></pre></p> <p>Crie o arquivo <code>app.def</code>: <pre><code>Bootstrap: docker
From: python:3.13-slim

%files
    app.py /app/app.py

%post
    mkdir -p /app
    pip install --no-cache-dir --upgrade pip

%environment
    export HOME=/app
    export PYTHONPATH=/app

%runscript
    exec python3 /app/app.py
</code></pre></p> <p>Build: <pre><code>apptainer build app.sif app.def
</code></pre></p> <p>Execute: <pre><code>apptainer run app.sif
</code></pre></p> <p>Crie o arquivo <code>postgres.def</code>: <pre><code>Bootstrap: docker
From: postgres:15

%labels
    Maintainer FundamentosDevOpsApptainer &lt;apptainer@fundamentosdevops.com&gt;
    Version 1.0

%environment
    export PGDATA=/var/lib/postgresql/data
    export POSTGRES_USER=usuario
    export POSTGRES_PASSWORD=senha

%runscript
    echo "Iniciando PostgreSQL..."
    exec docker-entrypoint.sh postgres

%startscript
    echo "Rodando PostgreSQL no modo startscript..."
    exec docker-entrypoint.sh postgres
</code></pre></p> <p>Build: <pre><code>apptainer build postgres.sif postgres.def
</code></pre></p> <p>Execute: <pre><code>mkdir -p ./pgdata
mkdir -p ./run_pg 
apptainer run --bind ./pgdata:/var/lib/postgresql/data --bind ./run_pg:/var/run/postgresql postgres.sif
</code></pre></p> <p>Crie o arquivo <code>index.html</code>: <pre><code>&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;
&lt;html lang="pt-br"&gt;
    &lt;head&gt;
        &lt;meta charset="UTF-8"&gt;
        &lt;title&gt;Nginx em Execução&lt;/title&gt;
        &lt;style&gt;
            body {
                font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
                background-color: #f4f4f4;
                color: #333;
                text-align: center;
                padding: 50px;
            }
            h1 {
                color: #2e8b57;
            }
            .container {
                background-color: white;
                padding: 40px;
                margin: auto;
                border-radius: 10px;
                box-shadow: 0px 0px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
                max-width: 600px;
            }
            footer {
                margin-top: 40px;
                font-size: 0.9em;
                color: #666;
            }
        &lt;/style&gt;
    &lt;/head&gt;
    &lt;body&gt;
        &lt;div class="container"&gt;
            &lt;h1&gt;🚀 Nginx está rodando com sucesso!&lt;/h1&gt;
            &lt;p&gt;Esta página faz parte da apresentação da disciplina &lt;strong&gt;Fundamentos de DevOps&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;p&gt;Servidor configurado e rodando via Apptainer 🎉&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;footer&gt;
            Fundamentos de DevOps - 2025
        &lt;/footer&gt;
    &lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;
</code></pre></p> <p>Crie o arquivo <code>nginx.def</code>: <pre><code>Bootstrap: docker
From: nginx
Includecmd: no

%files
index.html /usr/share/nginx/html/index.html

%startscript
nginx
</code></pre></p> <p>Build: <pre><code>sudo apptainer build nginx.sif nginx.def
</code></pre></p> <p>Inicie a instância: <pre><code>sudo apptainer instance start --writable-tmpfs nginx.sif web
</code></pre></p> <p>Liste as instâncias: <pre><code>sudo apptainer instance list
</code></pre></p>
